Class RakNet.UPnPResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • com.whirvis.jraknet.RakNet.UPnPResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable
    Enclosing class:
    RakNet

    public static class RakNet.UPnPResult
extends java.lang.Thread
    A Thread which runs in the background to allow for code relating to UPnP to be executed through the WaifUPnP without locking up the main thread.
    Since:
    JRakNet v2.11.0
    Author:
    Trent "Whirvis" Summerlin
    See Also:

        public void onFinish(java.lang.Runnable runnable)
